Data Aggregation System (DAS)
-----------------------------

An intelligent cache in front of ditributed data-services.
It fetches and aggregates data on demand upon user queries.
It serves as next generation of data discovery for
CMS experiment (http://cms.cern.ch)

For more information please consult doc section.

Installation
------------

*x64 machine with Scientific Linux CERN 5*

For easy instalation on Scientific Linux CERN 5 x64 machines (e.g. for Virtual machine service) see deployment.sh  (currently needs to be run manually with logout in middle)


*Other Linux (e.g. Debian, Ubuntu)*

See deploy_debian.sh

